sticker-542.name: Sticker | DavCost | Cologne 2015
sticker-542.description:
This item commemorates the 2015 ESL One Cologne CS:GO Championship.

This sticker can be applied to any weapon you own and can be scraped to look more worn. You can scrape the same sticker multiple times, making it a bit more worn each time, until it is removed from the weapon.

This sticker was autographed by professional player Vadim Vasilyev playing for Flipsid3 Tactics at ESL One Cologne 2015.\n\n50% of the proceeds from the sale of this sticker support the included players and organizations.
